The blue and yellow in Ukraineâ€™s flag each symbolize the blue sky and rich wheat. 
The woman in the artwork is the symbol of Nomad People who enjoy travel, while the broken heart expresses her sadness. 
 Us here at Weird Nomad Club sincerely hope for peace to be restored in Ukraine and all over the world. We want to assist by donating all funds from artwork sales towards helping Ukraine.
